OL,2,MForge & Craft / HackWimbledon
OL,4,E-2.374558309851807,52.04324498273803
OL,6,GForge & Craft is a husband-and-wife
OL,7,Gteam with a studio at Wimbledon Art
OL,8,GStudios in London. We explore art and
OL,9,Gdesign using technology (primarily pen
OL,10,Gplotters), and also tinker with
OL,11,Gelectronics, 3D printing, and crafting
OL,12,Gmachines between us. We're part of
OL,13,GHackWimbledon, a pop-up hackspace in
OL,14,Gsouth-west London.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
